title: Whitesnake - Greatest Hits
description:
Whitesnake&#039;s Greatest Hits is a compilation of Whitesnake&#039;s biggest hits from the 1980s. It features hit singles from their albums Slide It In, Whitesnake (the 1987 album) and Slip of the Tongue. The album also contains three tracks previously unavailable in the USA.

[edit] Track listing

   1. "Still of the Night" (from Whitesnake, 1987)
   2. "Here I Go Again" - Radio mix (from Whitesnake, 1987)
   3. "Is This Love" (from Whitesnake, 1987)
   4. "Love Ain&#039;t No Stranger" (from Slide It In, 1984)
   5. "Looking for Love" (from Whitesnake, 1987)
   6. "Now You&#039;re Gone" (from Slip of the Tongue, 1989)
   7. "Slide It In" (from Slide It In, 1984)
   8. "Slow an&#039; Easy" (from Slide It In, 1984)
   9. "Judgement Day" (from Slip of the Tongue, 1989)
  10. "You&#039;re Gonna Break My Heart Again" (from Whitesnake, 1987)
  11. "The Deeper the Love" (from Slip of the Tongue, 1989)
  12. "Crying in the Rain" - 1987 version (from Whitesnake, 1987)
  13. "Fool for Your Loving" - 1989 version (from Slip of the Tongue, 1989)
  14. "Sweet Lady Luck"
